### Home route
GET http://localhost:3000/


### Popular movies route
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/popular


### Now playing movies route
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/now-playing


### Search movies route
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/search?query=black


### Movie details route
GET http://localhost:3000/api/movies/1


### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users


### Create user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "jon",
  "password": "12345"
}


### Get users again after creating one
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users


### Bad route test
GET http://localhost:3000/api/does-not-exist